body:
Me. He&#039;s not talkative. He says few words. &quot;Behold&quot; Witness Truth&quot;

Even when Kled kills him he says &quot;He didn&#039;t say much but--&quot;

It takes a lot of the mystery away from him and that&#039;s one of the reasons why I picked him up. Let Camille and new Irelia go on and on.

I don&#039;t understand why Riots making everyone talk a whole a lot. I realize I can mute champ speech but hell, I don&#039;t want to play into Riots fantasy of Aatrox. I want mine damnit. I&#039;m all for an update but please keep the chattiness to a minimum. He&#039;s dark, mysterious thing of few words. PLEASE{{champion:266}}
